Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(OP)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.02,0:02:11.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露莉亚在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.52,0:02:16.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 看来有点做过头了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.01,0:02:19.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.54,0:02:22.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这时机真是无可挑剔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.99,0:02:28.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里的实验也结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.58,0:02:31.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回收这玩意儿后赶紧收队
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.79,0:02:32.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.15,0:02:35.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶！肆意妄为的混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.46,0:02:36.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们不单单污染了我们的海洋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.01,0:02:38.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还将我们的城镇搞成一团糟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.79,0:02:39.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直天理难…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.60,0:02:41.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.61,0:02:43.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要对他们做过分的事！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.46,0:02:44.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过分的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.93,0:02:46.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.33,0:02:48.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于这个岛的人来说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.82,0:02:52.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特别是那些年轻人来说 简直是天降横祸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.43,0:02:54.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你不来这座岛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.91,0:03:00.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们就既不会受伤害也不会被逮捕了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.32,0:03:06.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 就是因为你从我们那里逃跑了才会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.70,0:03:07.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.32,0:03:10.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你真心为了这里的人们着想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.63,0:03:13.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就老老实实的回到我们那里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.33,0:03:18.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想去你们那边
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.03,0:03:23.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么你想怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.01,0:03:26.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想和大家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.68,0:03:29.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想和古兰和卡塔莉娜一起继续旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.87,0:03:30.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.06,0:03:32.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旅行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.35,0:03:37.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你的这个愿望我既不会考虑 也不会允许
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.96,0:03:38.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.22,0:03:42.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你是星之民所遗留下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.40,0:03:46.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只为将一切破坏殆尽的工具
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.61,0:03:47.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工具？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.73,0:03:48.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.56,0:03:51.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就和这东西一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.95,0:03:59.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要扣动扳机就可以轻易伤人 夺人性命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.40,0:04:03.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是这样的一个工具
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.15,0:04:04.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是工具！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.08,0:04:06.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我不会做这种事的！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.02,0:04:07.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.16,0:04:13.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你忘记了自己是一个极其可怕的工具呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.66,0:04:19.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就我让你想起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.30,0:04:32.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你最初是何时看到这个光辉的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.25,0:04:34.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.30,0:04:37.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时除你之外还有其他实验体来着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.73,0:04:42.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些实验体最后如何了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.50,0:04:44.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你对他们做了什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.03,0:04:47.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该记得才对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.38,0:04:57.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想起来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.38,0:04:58.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.07,0:05:01.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是为了破坏而生的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.40,0:05:03.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你所能做的只有破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.13,0:05:05.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的存在意义仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.02,0:05:08.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为破坏而生的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.29,0:05:14.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不可以和那些一无所知 和平度日的人们在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.43,0:05:16.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能去大家那里…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.03,0:05:19.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你嘴里所谓的同伴也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.21,0:05:21.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你留在他们身边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.06,0:05:24.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们早晚会受尽折磨 遭遇不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.92,0:05:26.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古兰他们也不行？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.99,0:05:30.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会将他们所拥有的东西都破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.91,0:05:34.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连渣都不剩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.03,0:05:37.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,懂了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.08,0:05:40.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只能和我们在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.85,0:05:45.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为只有我们才能抑制你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.72,0:05:47.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要…我不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.12,0:05:50.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我想和大家一起！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.77,0:05:54.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手！还给我！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.25,0:06:04.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 快站起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.59,0:06:06.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别在这里浪费时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.93,0:06:15.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.55,0:06:18.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露莉亚！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.69,0:06:21.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古兰…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.53,0:06:25.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你对露莉亚做了什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.72,0:06:29.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是让她想起自己是什么东西而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.93,0:06:49.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.04,0:06:51.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是你吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.95,0:07:03.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又打算像那时那样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.69,0:07:07.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将自己以外的东西都破坏掉吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.27,0:07:07.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.73,0:07:20.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.72,0:07:22.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么了 露莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.92,0:07:25.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古兰！露莉亚！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.16,0:07:28.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.41,0:07:30.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 古兰 你受伤了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.09,0:07:32.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 露莉亚好像不太对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.73,0:07:34.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么了 露莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.46,0:07:37.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 不太妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.00,0:07:39.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么那个会出现在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.60,0:07:48.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古兰 你想做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.23,0:07:50.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须做点儿什么才行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.65,0:07:52.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不是做这些的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.67,0:07:54.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带上露莉亚 我们暂时先撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.29,0:07:54.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.43,0:07:59.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你受伤了 而且不能就这样放着露莉亚不管吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.88,0:08:06.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶紧离开这里！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.27,0:08:15.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了 赶紧去高处
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.76,0:08:46.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露莉亚！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.45,0:08:52.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 团长你又想乱来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.47,0:08:54.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作点啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.31,0:09:06.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.25,0:09:08.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这孩子挺让人担心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.62,0:09:10.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露莉亚！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.28,0:09:14.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之先将她转移到安全的地方去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.43,0:09:26.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.00,0:09:27.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.47,0:09:33.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起我 露莉亚如何了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.36,0:09:35.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 卡塔莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.51,0:09:36.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可以进去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.48,0:09:37.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.06,0:09:40.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露莉亚如何了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.66,0:09:47.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露莉亚…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.45,0:09:52.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这小妹妹到底怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.27,0:09:54.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然看上去像是在睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.30,0:09:57.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不管我怎么叫也叫不醒她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.03,0:10:01.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,治疗魔法也没用 为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.89,0:10:04.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道被刚才的怪物做了什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.19,0:10:06.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个魔物到底是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.08,0:10:09.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欧根 你应该知道些什么的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.79,0:10:10.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.53,0:10:11.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…刚刚那位？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.78,0:10:12.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫萝赛塔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.36,0:10:15.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算是他们的熟人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.21,0:10:22.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说欧根知道那东西是什么意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.83,0:10:24.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那条龙是这座岛的守护者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.19,0:10:29.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掌控生命之海的大星晶兽 利维坦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.87,0:10:33.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你久居在这里 应该有见过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.84,0:10:37.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是海洋的守护神？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.20,0:10:42.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想是因为帝国的实验导致海洋不断被污染
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.07,0:10:45.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从而使他变成了那个样子的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.05,0:10:50.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 露莉亚现在这个状况和利维坦有关联吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.45,0:10:52.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.55,0:10:56.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这与露莉亚自身所发生的异常没任何关系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.67,0:10:58.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说异常？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.03,0:11:00.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露莉亚到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.30,0:11:03.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她为了保护什么而封闭了内心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.44,0:11:06.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切断了一切呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.54,0:11:10.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来 魔法和药品都无法治愈她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.22,0:11:11.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？为什么会这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.29,0:11:14.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要如何才能唤醒她？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.72,0:11:16.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然有唤醒她的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.95,0:11:18.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但不容易
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.71,0:11:22.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且就算强行叫她起来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.72,0:11:26.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她可能又会想以另一种形式消失
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.77,0:11:27.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.80,0:11:30.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 不能就这样放着她不管
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.28,0:11:31.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.58,0:11:33.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是就算想为她做些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.29,0:11:36.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们连跟她对话的方法都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.88,0:11:39.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟她对话…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.59,0:11:41.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的如此吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.30,0:11:50.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定…古兰能行？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.41,0:11:53.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错！和她共享生命的你可以
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.05,0:11:57.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 这是只有你才能做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.31,0:12:00.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我才能做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.89,0:12:01.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.56,0:12:06.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的目的是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.19,0:12:10.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道又是黑骑士的手下？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.29,0:12:11.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说黑骑士？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.55,0:12:14.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我不期望你会实话实说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.08,0:12:16.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你在打什么算盘
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.34,0:12:21.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女人都会有秘密的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.25,0:12:27.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉卡姆 萝赛塔不是我们的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.42,0:12:32.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候 从海浪中将我们救起的是她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.87,0:12:34.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 在波特普利茲的时候也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.20,0:12:38.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢 你心意如何 团长？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.96,0:12:40.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管结果如何
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.37,0:12:42.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道让露莉亚苏醒的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.88,0:12:50.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎么做就交给你们决定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.26,0:12:55.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想好了就来告诉我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.41,0:13:01.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.85,0:13:03.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 古兰 要怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.85,0:13:05.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不赞成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.66,0:13:07.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎么说也太可疑了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.67,0:13:08.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欧根！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.58,0:13:09.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.45,0:13:10.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海水又发了变化
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.08,0:13:12.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且城里的水也产生了异变
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.08,0:13:15.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啧 一个接着一个的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.51,0:13:16.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去看看吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.63,0:13:17.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我陪你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.03,0:13:18.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.14,0:13:21.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古兰 你在这里休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.40,0:13:22.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡塔莉娜也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.75,0:13:23.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但…但是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.54,0:13:24.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.75,0:13:26.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你待在露莉亚的身边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.12,0:13:36.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当我到达露莉亚身边的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.81,0:13:39.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帝国的人好像已经对她做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.06,0:13:42.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伯梅伦…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.53,0:13:47.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说…「又打算像那时一样将自己以外的东西都破坏掉吗」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.86,0:13:49.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前也发生过这种事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.26,0:13:54.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡塔莉娜？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.83,0:13:56.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.95,0:14:02.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须得将我们和你相遇前发生的一些事告诉你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.54,0:14:04.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我相遇之前？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.40,0:14:05.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.51,0:14:07.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帝国对露莉亚做的实验
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.54,0:14:11.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其中就发生过类似的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.10,0:14:16.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帝国军为了开发武器
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.54,0:14:19.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对露莉亚和魔晶进行了研究
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.86,0:14:23.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在某个无人岛上进行魔晶实验的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.32,0:14:24.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生了失控事故
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.41,0:14:28.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被植入魔晶后发狂的魔物们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.40,0:14:30.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盯上露莉亚那一刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.93,0:14:31.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在此时…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.08,0:14:58.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我不知道露莉亚召唤出了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.85,0:15:00.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那股力量的余波
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.85,0:15:03.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让整个岛屿腐坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.41,0:15:10.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帝国马上决定囚禁露莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.53,0:15:16.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把她隔离…「保管」起来 以免她再次失控
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.45,0:15:19.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我则被选中去照顾她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.26,0:15:25.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候的露莉亚毫无表情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.17,0:15:29.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都觉得她像是一个机械
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.69,0:15:31.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.22,0:15:40.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露莉亚并非没有感情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.36,0:15:43.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她只是不知道如何去表达
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.31,0:15:49.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后我开始教她各种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.76,0:15:54.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露莉亚开始能够理解和感受到快乐和悲伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.36,0:15:56.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.15,0:15:59.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于我讲的故事 她开始抱有兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.58,0:16:03.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快便开始对外面的世界产生了向往
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.61,0:16:06.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当时就觉得如果能离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.21,0:16:08.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在外面的世界里自由生活的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.42,0:16:10.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是我决定…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.28,0:16:14.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后来露莉亚见到了你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.32,0:16:16.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通过和你相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.36,0:16:21.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露莉亚应该学到了我没能教给她的重要的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.51,0:16:23.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露莉亚每天晚上都会跟我说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.93,0:16:28.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她和你还有伊欧做了什么以及看到了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.69,0:16:29.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她非常开心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.83,0:16:32.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对此感到很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.06,0:16:39.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我却没有保护好露莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.33,0:16:42.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候我什么都没做到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.21,0:16:46.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 卡塔莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.73,0:16:47.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.35,0:16:49.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.21,0:16:52.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些应该全都由我来承担的！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.92,0:16:55.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但为什么受伤的会是你们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.42,0:16:57.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡塔莉娜？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.34,0:17:02.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露莉亚为什么要受这样的苦才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.86,0:17:13.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能感受到露莉亚的感情 并很爱护她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.77,0:17:16.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这对于从那个什么都没有的房间里走出来的露莉亚来说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.66,0:17:18.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是多大的救赎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.86,0:17:23.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古兰 你也去休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.53,0:17:24.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.90,0:17:27.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我待在露莉亚的身边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.02,0:17:35.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是古兰吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.39,0:17:36.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.68,0:17:37.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露莉亚如何了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.16,0:17:41.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.59,0:17:48.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俺说 你在烦恼什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.94,0:17:54.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能和露莉亚对话 我该说些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.36,0:18:00.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且她到底想保护什么才这样一觉不醒的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.23,0:18:03.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俺不可能知道的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.98,0:18:06.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟不管是俺还是你都不是露莉亚嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.40,0:18:08.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.49,0:18:14.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以先听听她的话如何
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.54,0:18:18.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她肯定有一些对所有人都说不出口的烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.60,0:18:21.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果问的人是你 她应该会说的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.63,0:18:27.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你们共享生命嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.63,0:18:31.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以这正是你才能做的事 不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.75,0:18:35.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.90,0:18:38.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好和露莉亚谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.30,0:18:40.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把你的想法告诉她的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.34,0:18:42.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俺觉得露莉亚一定会想回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.67,0:18:44.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.60,0:18:46.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 碧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.18,0:18:47.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.90,0:18:54.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俺知道 你一定能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.99,0:18:56.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.35,0:19:01.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是跟我走会遭遇什么没人会知道哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.88,0:19:03.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道 没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.01,0:19:05.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我带你走…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.14,0:19:09.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带你们到能拯救她的星晶兽的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.31,0:19:10.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星晶兽…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.09,0:19:13.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我没办法保证会发生什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.95,0:19:16.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的生命是露莉亚分给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.34,0:19:19.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我一定会救她的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.33,0:19:22.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.47,0:19:25.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算接受那个女人的提议吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.15,0:19:27.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.19,0:19:28.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.60,0:19:32.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟目前我们也没有其他救露莉亚的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.43,0:19:34.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能赌赌看了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.46,0:19:37.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.50,0:19:40.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,团长你决定去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.32,0:19:43.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就把你们安全地送到哪 这就是舵手的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.71,0:19:44.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉卡姆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.98,0:19:45.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.60,0:19:48.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小伙子 不用客气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.20,0:19:50.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想做什么就做什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.61,0:19:54.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天塌下来有我们顶住
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.65,0:19:56.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我们大人的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.67,0:19:57.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.45,0:20:00.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.17,0:20:04.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.86,0:20:05.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊欧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.59,0:20:07.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凭什么你们就这样决定了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.90,0:20:09.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.37,0:20:11.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是碰巧你不在…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.37,0:20:13.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了！露莉亚是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.05,0:20:16.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想为她出点儿力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.75,0:20:18.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像师父帮了我一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.82,0:20:20.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 我知道了 你冷静点！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.72,0:20:22.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很冷静啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.24,0:20:24.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一定会去的！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.29,0:20:31.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抛下我就出发的话一定不会原谅你们的！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.89,0:20:33.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.50,0:20:36.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熊孩子真吵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.50,0:20:37.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么关系呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.26,0:20:43.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不算团结 但你们的方向都是一致的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.45,0:20:44.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话是没错啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.43,0:20:49.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 伊欧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.85,0:21:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受你照顾了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.41,0:21:01.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要出发了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.72,0:21:04.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 全都完事后我们会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.50,0:21:06.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以大叔你也别挂掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.79,0:21:09.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真敢说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.81,0:21:11.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.17,0:21:13.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.24,0:21:15.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝你们好运
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.02,0:21:20.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.79,0:21:23.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听到消息后赶紧跑过来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.19,0:21:26.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到发生了这么大的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.61,0:21:28.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 正如你所见到的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.75,0:21:30.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 为了修复城镇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.63,0:21:32.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就麻烦你四处筹集各种物资了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.46,0:21:37.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 我也是尽自己所能罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.80,0:21:39.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了 我们出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.65,0:21:41.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 不能这样磨蹭下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.37,0:21:43.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.84,0:21:46.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萝赛塔阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.90,0:21:48.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦你带路了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.70,0:21:51.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我们出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.72,0:21:54.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前往郁郁葱葱的岛屿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.30,0:21:55.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁马西群岛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.30,0:21:55.88,Default,NTP,0,120,0,,{\fs30}Lumacie
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.44,0:21:57.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁马西群岛……
